            <option letter="d">The Pure Food and Drug Act</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Nation's anti-saloon rhetoric exemplified temperance movement arguments that led to the Eighteenth Amendment establishing Prohibition.</explanation>
